08.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024_mileycyrus_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024_mileycyrus_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024_mileycyrus_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/miley-cyrus">麦莉·赛勒斯</a>将于明天（2 月 4 日）在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美颁奖典礼</a>上演唱她的热门单曲《Flowers》。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/miley-cyrus-endless-summer-vacation-review-lyrics-tracklist-3409627">麦莉·赛勒斯 - 《无尽的暑假》评论：强有力的权力回收</a></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://variety.com/2024/music/news/miley-cyrus-flowers-grammy-awards-1235896166/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《综艺》报道</em></a>，这位在颁奖典礼上获得六项奖项提名的歌手将自去年一月发行以来首次在电视上表演这首歌。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/miley-cyrus-performs-flowers-first-time-3547478">去年11月，她在洛杉矶马尔蒙城堡的私人演出中首次播出</a>了这首单曲。它正在角逐格莱美奖的年度歌曲和年度唱片。</p><p>在宣布获得 2024 年格莱美奖六个类别的提名后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lana-del-rey-mark-ronson-olivia-rodrigo-and-more-react-to-grammy-nominations-3536375">赛勒斯赞扬了其他女性提名者</a>。 “祝贺所有今年的格莱美提名者，”她当时写道。 “看到女性赢得并统治音乐界让我感到自豪。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="麦莉赛勒斯 - 花（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/G7KNmW9a75Y?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>她将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish)</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/travis-scott">、</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo</a> )、杜阿·利帕 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a> )、特拉维斯·斯科特<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/travis-scott">(Travis Scott</a> ) 和伯纳·博伊<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/burna-boy">(Burna Boy)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/u2">U2</a> （ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/u2-to-livestream-performance-from-las-vegas-sphere-for-2024-grammys-3578092">将在拉斯维加斯的 Sphere 进行首次现场直播）</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joni-mitchell">乔尼·米切尔 (Joni Mitchell)</a>一起表演，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/joni-mitchell-to-perform-at-2024-grammys-3578391">后者将在格莱美颁奖典礼上表演。这是她六年多的职业生涯中的第一次</a>。</p><p>本周早些时候，已确认<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sza-perform-2024-grammys-this-weekend-3578926">也将在洛杉矶 Crypto.com Arena 举行的活动中表演</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tracy-chapman">特雷西·查普曼 (Tracy Chapman)</a>也有望在格莱美颁奖典礼上与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/luke-combs">卢克·库姆斯 (Luke Combs)</a>一起表演<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tracy-chapman-reportedly-set-to-perform-fast-car-with-luke-combs-at-grammys-3580446">《Fast Car》</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/trevor-noah-to-host-2024-grammys-3559098#:~:text=Trevor%20Noah%20has%20been%20announced,in%20which%20he%20has%20hosted.&amp;text=The%20former%20Daily%20Show%20host,in%20both%202019%20and%202020.">特雷弗·诺亚将连续第四年主持该奖项</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift</a> )、SZA、维多利亚<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/victoria-monet">·莫奈 (Victoria Monet</a> ) 和菲比·布里杰斯 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phoebe-bridgers">Phoebe Bridgers)</a>领衔今年的提名—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/here-are-all-the-grammys-2024-nominations-3536101" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在此处查看完整名单</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/miley-cyrus-is-reportedly-set-to-perform-flowers-at-2024-grammys-this-weekend-3581877">据报道，麦莉·赛勒斯 (Miley Cyrus) 将于本周末在 2024 年格莱美颁奖典礼上表演《Flowers》，该节目</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
